      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/684fa7a7dba37.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/684fa7a9c210b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/684fa7a787e3a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/684fa7af044ff.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/684fa79c781fa.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; BNP file added&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Thanks to &lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1921916"&gt;@Mei_R      &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;now the mod has it's bnp file, for those who need it :D the best unbreakable weapons mod for BOTW ...but updated lol&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: BNP file added to downloads section&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;Hello, from time to time i like to port obscure mods i tend to find on the web, i present you proper unbreakable weapons mod (they don't have durability+ modifier like other mods do) now weapons are trully unbreakable, wanna use a treebranch all the game ? now you can do ! &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;also i included a new proper ng+ savegame (master mode save, to use with normal mode just paste game_data.sav) with this save you still need to do the complete tutorial to get the runes but :&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;the ng+ includes &lt;br&gt;- Paraglider from the start&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Master Cycle Zero from the start (once you get the sheikah slate from the first guidance stone, open map, and select the byke rune from L button menu in case the rune menu doesn't open up with dpad up)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-3 stamina wheels / 3 hearts (you can buy other 9 hearts at the demon statue in Hateno to get the master sword without doing more shrines than the first four at the plateau or any divine beast)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- all locations discovered (included shrines) BUT no easy fast travel (enabling shrines teleport tend to break quest, also softlocks you if you try to do certain shrine quest too, also i find it better to not fast travel since the start)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- some items so you can cook stats boosting meals/camp &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-999 rupees&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-True Hylian Shield 1000 block points (you can now block golden lynel explosions without any stagger)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Ancient Shield intended for shield surf (shield surf up, guardian/ancient shields are way more slippery than the radiant shield)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Boosted Ancient Sword &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- all arrows 999 except ancient arrows (they are too op, only 100 ancient arrows from the go)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- savage lynel bow 5 arrow burst, twilight bow 60 dmg (intended for solving puzzles)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- clothes for heat/cold/lava areas/climbing/swiming (zora greaves/helm) + 2 bonus sets from the go (surprise)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- 900 koroks discovered with their seeds (what a waste of time tbh)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- BE WARY !!! the strongest enemy variations are roaming now (in master mode you can encounter golden enemies at the plateau)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- complete compendium (you still need to repair the sheikah slate at hateno, but once you do, all compendium pictures are gonna be there)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;of course i added a lot of stuff while keeping other things unchanged ... due to how they can break the whole game, or due to how they can make the ng+ experience kind of shallow &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;just in case it doesn't seem clear, if you want to get the master sword, complete the first 4 tutorial shrines at plateau , trade those spirit orbs for a heart container, reach the demon statue at Hateno and buy the other 9 with it (in any case you are gonna end up with 13 hearts, once you defeat all divine beast you are gonna have 17, getting the other 13 is a matter of completing shrines)</description>
