 torch/ korok leaf and all the elemental weapons, all with crazy damage for all of them. Also with the pretty much activated OHB (65536 damage). 10 Savage lynel swords all with every modifier the game lets me allowed also on this tab, shown on the save editor weapons screenshot.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Sheilds - Similar layout to weapons, with the Ancient sheild with guard up, in my opinion best weapon in the game, guardian shield++ with -65535 friction, the game treats it like -1 sadly, and hylian sheild with +65535 guard, best sheild in the game with 2147483647 friction as well, basically infinite and great for getting skew I guess. There are also a couple other cool sheilds in this tab of course. Also with 5 Savage lynel sheilds with +65535 damage, kills everything in line of parrying, and hylian sheilds with again all modifiers the game lets me that aren't the normal ones, just like the layout for weapons.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Bows - a bunch of modified bows of light and the same modifiers on 3 great eagle bows if you want to use normal arrows (modifiers work a little differently from bow of light from the base 3x shot), and 7 savage lynel bows with 10 shot. Also 65535 every arrow (&lt;i&gt;fully &lt;/i&gt;capped out), that was a pain to get working in the hex editor.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Armor - all amiibo armor and dlc armor, and &lt;i&gt;most&lt;/i&gt; normal armor. The game has 107 pieces total, but only 100 can be stored. There is none of the  monster masks (lizalfos, bokoblin, moblin, and lynel, but still majora's mask though), no warm doublet, and no old shirt and its well worn trousers counterpart.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Items - 999 every item + Milk 0x, a completely broken item literally hidden in the games code.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Food - 999 every numbered cooked/frozen thing except rushroom, ironshroom, silent shroom, and razorshroom, the cooked foods with the least health given, as well as crit cooked 5 big hearty radishes (best health regen), and crit cooked 5 endura carrots (best stamina regen), along with a hidden 999 counter on both them, eating one shows x1 for 998 more, until it's gone.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Key items - all temporary and permanant items in the game. anything numbered is capped at 999, and I will say right now the divine beast emblems were a PAIN to get.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;As seen in the editor screenshots, every item has 6553500 durability (literally infinite - hylian shield has 80000). Also in the save editor home screenshot, you can see 65535x uses for ravioli's gale, urbosa's fury, and daruk's protection, so infinite of those I guess. Everything in this mod can be extracted if you want and ran through the online save editor &gt;&lt;a href="https://www.marcrobledo.com/savegame-editors/zelda-botw/" target="_blank"&gt;Here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;. &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;KEEP IN MIND -&lt;/span&gt; When ran through the editor some things can break as that editor has caps that needed to bebroken through with the hex editor after exporting. By the way i used Hxd for editing the .sav directly, great tool. FINAL NOTE - I just realized while tying this i didn't touch on my horses, so have fun with cow I guess.&lt;br&gt;</description>
