i's Tornado&lt;br&gt;•&amp;nbsp;Mipha's Grace = Mipha's Prayer&lt;br&gt;•&amp;nbsp;Urbosa's Fury = Urbosa's Wrath&lt;br&gt;•&amp;nbsp;The sword that seals the darkness = The Blade of Evil's Bane&lt;br&gt;•&amp;nbsp;The phrase "goro" is left intact, though Yunobo says "コロ" (koro), not "ごろ" (goro).&lt;br&gt;•&amp;nbsp;The quest titled "Slated for Upgrades" has been translated to "Unlock more Power".&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You can watch the mod on my PeerTube instance:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://peertube.linuxrocks.online/a/rollspelsroger/video-channels" target="_blank"&gt;https://peertube.linuxrocks.online/a/rollspelsroger/video-channels&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;It's also available for the Wii U-version of the game here:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/652995"&gt;https://gamebanana.com/mods/652995&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod was made with build 1.6.0 and DLC 3.0.</description>
