      <guid isPermaLink="false">d5d9af5b8e20175fc6bbbb982cc6d7636ec007d9</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 23:25:51 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69efeeda4fbe0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69efecc2e09b5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69efecc2e0276.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69efecc2dc7f9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69efecc2dd1d5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;Modifies a handful of the OG link tunics obtained from scanning Amiibos and gives them elemental protections and abilities like that of some other armour sets in the game.&lt;br&gt;I really made the mod just to my liking, so there isn't much rhyme or reason to why/what i changed, but i feel like some may also enjoy it.&lt;br&gt;Primarily created to allow myself to always look like OG link (or at least one of them) while exploring the world and without having to worry about changing into the regions clothes.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;Twilight Set&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;Cap (0-1 star):&amp;nbsp;ResistElectric 1&amp;nbsp;(reduce damage from electric element)&lt;br&gt;Cap (2-3 star):&amp;nbsp;ResistElectric 2 (reduce damage from electric element)&lt;br&gt;Cap (4 star):&amp;nbsp;ResistLightning 1 (immune to lightning strkies)&lt;br&gt;Tunic (0-4 star):&amp;nbsp;ClimbSpeed 1 (increases&amp;nbsp;climbing speed)&lt;br&gt;Tunic (2-3 star):&amp;nbsp;ClimbSpeed 2&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;(increases&amp;nbsp;climbing speed)&lt;br&gt;Tunic (4 star):&amp;nbsp;ClimbSpeed 3&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;(increases&amp;nbsp;climbing speed)&lt;br&gt;Trousers (0-1 star):&amp;nbsp;Quietness 1 (decreases movement sound)&lt;br&gt;Trousers (2-3 star):&amp;nbsp;Quietness 2&amp;nbsp;(decreases movement sound)&lt;br&gt;Trousers (4 star):&amp;nbsp;Quietness 3&amp;nbsp;(decreases movement sound)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;Wind Set&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;Cap (0-4 star):&amp;nbsp;SwimSpeed 1 (increases swimming speed)&lt;br&gt;Tunic (0-4 star):&amp;nbsp;SwimSpeed 1&amp;nbsp;(increases swimming speed) + ability to climb waterfalls&lt;br&gt;Trousers (0-4 star):&amp;nbsp;SwimSpeed 1&amp;nbsp;(increases swimming speed)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;Sky Set&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;Cap (0-4 star):&amp;nbsp;ResistCold&amp;nbsp;(allows withstanding cold temperatures like hebra mountains)&lt;br&gt;Tunic (0-4 star):&amp;nbsp;ResistCold&amp;nbsp;(allows withstanding cold temperatures like hebra mountains)&lt;br&gt;Trousers (0-4 star): SnowMove 1&amp;nbsp;(increases movement speed in snow)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hero Set&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;Cap (0-4 star): ResistHot 1 (allows withstanding hot temperatures like gerudo desert)&lt;br&gt;Tunic (0-4 star):&amp;nbsp;ResistHot 1&amp;nbsp;(allows withstanding hot temperatures like gerudo desert)&lt;br&gt;Trousers (0-4 star): SandMove 1 (increases movement speed in sand)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;All sets gain the same armour rating to match &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/443023"&gt;Hyrule Rebalance&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;0 star: 2 defence&lt;br&gt;1 star: 3&amp;nbsp;defence&lt;br&gt;2 star: 4&amp;nbsp;defence&lt;br&gt;3 star: 5&amp;nbsp;defence&lt;br&gt;4 star: 6&amp;nbsp;defence&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;All sets also still have the same set bonus as original.</description>
