    <item>
      <title>BOTW DS4 UI Mod v2 - Western Layout</title>
      <author>Velkyn</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/659253</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/659253#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">8b64cb10013cd8bd715879ab92267866daeb16d6</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 02:30:41 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6a0b59c33acc2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69e3be8834e06.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69b17d0a1f588.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; UKMM version added&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Adjustment&lt;/em&gt;: Reworked description and added due credits.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Adjustment&lt;/em&gt;: Replaced prompts with colorful ones and added a missing L2 icon (when approaching an NPC on horseback)&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Here is the original body of text, from &lt;/b&gt;&lt;a class="MemberLink" href="https://gamebanana.com/members/5188618" data-id="member_5188618"&gt;bitasuperactive&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/submissions/contributions/5188618" class="CreditsLink" aria-label="Contributions"&gt;&lt;spriteicon class="SubnavigatorIcon ContributionsIcon SelectedElement"&gt;&lt;/spriteicon&gt;&lt;/a&gt; :&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;"I have NOT created this mod.&lt;/b&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a mod for Yuzu/Citron (romfs) that replaces the entire Switch UI with the Xbox/PS UI. The mod also replaces all tips and tutorials with the Xbox/PS UI ones.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;All the credits to the original anonymous author which work was found on &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/linkfilter?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fyuzu%2Fcomments%2F17o7d7x%2Fyuzu_xbox_ui_mod_for_botw%2F%3Ftl%3Des-es&amp;follow=true" target="_blank"&gt;this &lt;/a&gt;reddit thread.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The purpose of this post is to spread the mod, which was hard to find for me. Cheers."&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;It was made with a standard layout, and even with the help of sys-con (&lt;a href="https://github.com/o0Zz/sys-con?tab=readme-ov-file" target="_blank" class="underline"&gt;https://github.com/o0Zz/sys-con?tab=readme-ov-file&lt;/a&gt;), despite it working correctly in the menus and tips, the interaction prompts (like harvesting an apple or talking to an NPC) used to stay on the Nintendo layout instead of swapping to the DS4 one.&lt;br&gt;Now they do swap correctly.</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/botw_ds4_ui_mod_v2_-_western_layout_ukkm.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/botw_ds4_ui_mod_v2_-_western_layout_sav.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <category>GUIs</category>
      <category>GUIs</category>
    </item>
